BAND INFO

QUOTE
Mortal Love is a Norwegian gothic metal band which is currently signed to Massacre Records. Their sound makes combined use of soprano and tenor vocals, whilst placing emphasis on a consistent rhythm section, piano and synthesizer melodies and slower tempos. The predominant subject of their lyrics is love, which may be due to the fact that their first three releases are intended as a trilogy, as can be observed from combining the titles of the albums (All the Beauty, I Have Lost and Forever Will Be Gone). The band released the final album of the trilogy on 22 September 2006.
